<paragraph pageId="135" pageNumber="136">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="135" pageNumber="136">This species is dedicated to the Ecuadorian biologist Patricia Ortiz who tragically passed away in her second home of Monteverde, Puntarenas, Costa Rica. Pati was one of the best and most passionate naturalists I have had the fortune to meet.</paragraph>
